# - Config file for the genvtx package
# It defines the following variables
#  genvtx_INCLUDE_DIRS - include directories for genvtx
#  genvtx_LIBRARY      - libraries to link against
#  genvtx_LIBRARIES    - libraries to link against

### No support:
#  genvtx_BIO_LIBRARY  - library targets to link against (Boost I/O library)
#  genvtx_REFLECTION_LIBRARY - library targets to link against (reflection library)
#  genvtx_WITH_BIO     - flag for Boost/Serialization I/O DLL (a.k.a. 'bio')
#  genvtx_WITH_REFLECTION  - flag for reflection DLL

